This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for semantic parsing, which are typically covered in the arXiv categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks and deep learning, which are relevant to the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper includes experiments with image-based instructions, which could be relevant to computer vision (cs.CV).
